hadiths[73]{hadithnumber,text}:
1788,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney kabhi khuwan (mez waghera) par nahin khaya, na chhoti tashtariyon aur pyaliyon mein khaya, aur na aap key liye kabhi patli roti pakaai gaee. Yunus kehtey hain : mainey Qatada sey puchha : phir kis chiz par khatey they? kaha : unhi dastarkhanon par. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- Muhammad bin Bashaar kehtey hain : ye Yunus , Yunus Iskaf hain, 3- abdul-waaris bin Saeed ney basanad ( سعيد بن أبي عروبة an قتادة an أنس an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) isi jaisi hadees riwayat ki hai."
1789,"hamney maqam marruz-zohraan main eik khargosh ka peecha kya, Sahaba kiram uskey peechey dodey , mainey usey paa liya aur pakad liya , phir usey abu-Talha key paas laya , unhoney us ko pathar sey zibeh kya aur mujhey uski raan dey kar Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas bheja, chunanche aap ney usey khaya. Raavi Hisham bin Zaid kehtey hain : mainey ( Raavi hadees apney dada Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey) puchha : kya aap ney isey khaya? kaha : aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney isey qubul kya padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Jabir, Ammaar, Muhammad bin Safwan (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, wo khargosh khaney mein koi muzaaeqa nahin samajhtey hain, 4- jabke baaz ehle-ilm khargosh khaney ko makrooh samajhtey hain, ye log kehtey hain : usey (yani mada khargosh ko) haiz ka khoon aata hai."
1790,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey goh khaney key barey mein puchha gaya? to aap ney farmaya : ''main na to usey khata hun aur na haram kehta hun '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein umr , abu Saeed Khudri , ibne-Abbas , Sabit bin Wadiaa, Jabir aur Abdur-Rehman bin Hasna (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- goh khaney key silsiley mein ehle-ilm ka ikhtilaf hai, baaz ehle-ilm Sahaba ney rukhsat di hai, 4- aur baaz ney isey makrooh samjha hai, ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey marvi hai, wo kehtey hain : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key dastar khuwan par goh khaya gaya, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney tabaii karahat ki bina par usey chhod diya ."
1791,"mainey Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : kya lakadbaggha bhi shikar hai? unhoney kaha : haan , mainey puchha : usey kha sakta hun? kaha : haan , mainey puchha : kya ye Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya hai? kaha : haan . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Yahya Qataan kehtey hain : Jareer bin Hazim ney ye hadees is sanad sey riwayat ki hai : Abdullah bin Ubaid bin Umer ney ibne-Abi Ammar sey , ibne-Abi Ammar ney Jabir sey , Jabir ney umr (Raziallahu anhu) key qol sey riwayat ki hai, ibne-Jurej ki hadees ziyada sahih hai, 3- baaz ehle-ilm ka yehi mazhab hai, wo log lakadbaggha khaney mein koi harj nahin samajhtey hain. Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai, 4- Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey lakadbaggha khaney ki karaahat key silsiley main eik hadees aai hai, lekin iski sanad qawi nahin hai, 5- baaz ehle-ilm ney bijjo khaney ko makrooh samjha hai, ibne-Mubarak ka bhi yehi qol hai."
1792,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey lakadbaggha khaney key barey mein puchha , to aap ney farmaya : '' bhala koi lakadbaggha khata hai? mainey aap sey bhediye key barey mein poochha, to aap ney farmaya : '' bhala koi nek aadmi bhediya khata hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ki sanad qawi nahin hai hum usey Abdul-Karim abi Umayya key wastey sey sirf Ismail bin Muslim ki riwayat sey jantey hain, 2- baaz muhaddeseen ney Ismail aur Abdul-Karim abi Umayya key barey mein kalam kya hai, ( hadees ki sanad mein mazkur ( ye Abdul-Karim , Abdul-Karim bin Qais bin abi al-Makhariq hain, 3- aur Abdul-Karim bin Malik Jazri Suqa hain."
1793,"Hazrat Jabir Raziallahu anhu kehtey hain ke Rasoolullah sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamen ghodey ka gosht khilaya aur gadhey ka gosht khaney sey mana farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- isi tarah bahut sey logon ney isey Jabir sey Amr bin Dinar ki taraf sey riwayat kya hai, 3- Hammad bin Zaid ney usey Amr bin Dinar sey riwayat kya hai. sirf riwayat ki gaee hai, ibne-Uena ki riwayat ziyada sahih hai, 4- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey suna : Sufiyan bin uena hafizey mein Hammad bin Zaid sey ziyada shayer hain, 5- iskey barey mein Asma Raziallahu anha binte-abi Bakr sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1794,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ghazwa khaibar key moqey par aurton sey nikahe-mutaa karney sey padhi. aur paaltu gadhon key gosht sey mana farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- hum sey Saeed bin Abdur-Rehman makhzoomi ney basanad (سفيان an الزهري an عبد الله والحسن) ney usi jaisi hadees bayan ki, Abdullah o Hasan dono Muhammad bin Hanfiya key betey hain, aur Abdullah bin Muhammad al-Hanfiya ki kunniyat abu-Hashim hai, Zohri kehtey hain : un dono mein ziyada pasandida Hasan bin Muhammad bin Hanfiya hain, phir unhoney ibne-Uena sey riwayat karney waley Saeed bin Abdur-Rehman key ilawa doosrey logon ney kaha hai : un dono mein ziyada pasandida Abdullah bin Muhammad bin Hanfiya hain."
1795,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney ghazwaey khaibar key din har kachli (nukiley) daant waley darinda janwer, « مجثمة  aur paaltu gadhey ko haram qarar diya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- abdul-Azeez bin Muhammad aur doosrey logon ney bhi usey Muhammad bin Amr sey riwayat kya hai aur un logon ney sirf eik jumla bayan kya hai (نهى رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم an كل ذي ناب من السباع) '' yani sirf nukiley daant waley darindon ka zikr kya, mujassma aur paaltu gadhey ka zikr nahin kya'', padhi. 2- is bab mein Ali , Jabir , Bara , ibne-Abi Aufi , Anas , Arbaz bin Saariya , Abu-Solba , ibne-Umar aur abu Saeed Khudri (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1796,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey majoos ki haandiyon ( bartanon ( key barey mein puchha gaya, to aap ney farmaya : '' unhen dho kar saaf karo aur un mein khana pakaao, aur aap ney har nukiley daant waley darindey janwer sey mana farmaya ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Abu-Solba ki riwayat sey mashhur hai, un sey ye hadees dusri sanad sey bhi aai hai, 2- Abu-Solba ka naam Jarsum hai, unhen Jurham aur Nashib bhi kaha gaya hai, 2- ye hadees (عن أبي قلابة an أبي أسماء الرحبي an أبي ثعلبة) ki sanad sey bhi bayan ki gaee hai."
1797,"unhoney sawal kya : Allah key Rasool ! hum log ehle-kitab ki sar zamin mein rehtey hain, kya ham unki haandiyon mein khana pakaaein aur unkey bartanon mein pani piyen? to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' agar tumhen uskey ilawa koi bartan na mil sakey to usey pani sey dho lo'' , phir unhoney puchha : Allah key Rasool ! hum shikar wali sar zamin mein rehtey hain kaisey keren? aap ney farmaya : '' jab tum apna sadhaaya huwa kutta rawana karo aur is par «Bismillah» padh lo phir wo shikar maar daley to usey khaao, aur agar kutta sadhaaya huwa na ho aur shikar zibeh kar diya jaey to usey khaao aur jab tum teer maaro aur is par «bismillah» padh lo phir us sey shikar ho jaey to usey khaao''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1798,"eik chuhiya ghi mein gir kar mar gaee, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey uskey barey mein puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya : ''usey aur jo kuch chiknai uskey ird-gird hai usey phenk do padhi. aur (bacha huwa) ghi kha lo''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ye hadees is sanad sey bhi aai hai «Zohri an Ubaidullah an ibne-Abbas an-nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » , padhi. raawiyon ney is mein «an Memuna» ka wasta nahin bayan kya hai, 3- Memuna key wastey sey ibne-Abbas ki hadees ziyada sahih hai, 4- Maamar ney b-tareeq : « Zohri , an ibne-Abi Hurera , an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » jaisi hadees riwayat ki hai, ye hadees (sanad ( ghair mehfooz hai, mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey suna ke Maamar ki hadees jisey wo (عن الزهري an سعيد ابن المسيب an أبي هريرة an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) ki sanad sey riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey uskey barey mein puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya : '' jab ghi jama huwa ho to chuhiya aur uskey ird-gird ka ghi phenk do aur agar pighla huwa ho to uskey qarib na jaao ''ye khata hai, is mein Maamar sey khata hui hai, sahih Zohri hi ki hadees hai jo (عن عبيد الله an ابن عباس an ميمونة) ki sanad sey aai hai padhi. , 5- is bab mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1799,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhu sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : tum mein sey koi baaein haath sey na khaye aur na baaein haath sey piye، kyonkey shetan baaein haath sey khata hai aur baaein haath sey peeta hai, imaam. Tirmizi kehtey hain ke 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- isi tarah Malik aur ibne-Uena ney Zohri ki sanad sey riwayat ki hai, Maamar aur Aqeel ney usey Sulem bin Abdullah sey Zohri ki sanad key sath riwayat kya hai. Malik aur ibne-Uena ki riwaayatein ziyada sahih hain, 3- is barey mein Jabir, umr bin abi Salma, Salma bin Akwa, Anas bin Malik aur Hafsa Raziallah anhum sey bhi ahaadees aai hain."
1800,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab tum mein sey koi khaye to daain haath sey khaye aur daain haath sey piye isliye ke shetan apney baaein hath sey khata hai aur baaein hath sey peeta hai''.
1801,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab tum mein sey koi khana khaye to apni ungliyan chaat ley, kyonkey wo nahin janta ke un mein sey kis ungli mein barkat hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey is hadees key barey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : Abdul-Azeez ki ye hadees , mukhtalif key قبیل sey hai, aur sirf in ki riwayat sey hi jaani jati hai. 3- is bab mein Jabir , Kaab bin Malik aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain. hum isey is sanad sey sirf Suhel ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
1802,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab tum mein sey koi khana khaye aur niwaala gir jaey to is mein sey jo napasand samjhey usey hata dey, isey phir kha ley, isey shetan key liye na chhodey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein Anas sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1803,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab khana khatey to apni teeno ungliyon ko chaat'tey they, aap ney farmaya : ''jab tum mein sey kisi ka niwala gir jaey to us sey gard aur ghubar door karey aur usey kha ley, isey shetan key liye na chhodey'' ,aap ney hamein plate chaatney ka hukm diya aur farmaya : ''tum log nahin jantey ke tumharey khaney key kis hissey mein barkat rakhi hui hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai."
1804,"hamarey paas Nabeeshal-Khair aaye, hum log eik piyaley mein khana kha rahey they, to unhoney hum sey bayan kiya ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo shakhs piyaley mein khaye phir usey chaate to piyala uskey liye istighfar karta hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf Muallaa bin Rashid ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 2- Yazeed bin Harun aur kaee Aaimmae hadees ney bhi ye hadees Muallaa bin Rashid sey riwayat ki hai."
1805,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' barkat khaney key bich mein nazil hoti hai, isliye tum log uskey kinaron sey khaao , bech sey mat khaao.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- aur sirf Ata bin Saaib ki riwayat sey maroof hai, isey Shoba aur Sory ney bhi Ata bin Saaib sey riwayat kiya hai. 3- is bab mein ibne-Umar sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1806,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo shakhs in mein sey lahsun khaye, ya lahsun , piyaz aur gandanaa khaye wo hamari masjidon mein hamarey qarib na aaye.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein umr , abu-Ayyub , Abu-Hurera , abu Saeed Khudri , Jabir bin Samura , Qurra bin Ayas Muzni aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1807,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ( hijrat key baad) abu-Ayyub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) key ghar thehrey , aap jab bhi khana khatey to uska kuchh hissa abu-Ayyub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) key paas bhejtey , aap ney eik din ( pura ( khana ( wapis ( bheja , is mein sey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney kuchh nahin khaya , jab abu-Ayyub Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aaye aur aap sey iska zikr kiya to aap ney farmaya : ''us mein lahsun hai? '' , unhoney puchha : Allah key Rasool ! kya wo haram hai? aap ney farmaya : ''nahin , lekin uski bo ki wajeh sey main isey napasand karta hun.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1808,Lahsun khaney sey mana kiya gaya hai siwaye iskey ke wo pakka huwa ho.
1809,"Ali (Raziallahu anhu) lahsun khana makrooh samajhtey they, siwaye iskey ke wo pakka huwa ho. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ki sanad ziyada qawi nahin hai, ye Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ka qol hai. 2- Shareek bin Hanbal key wastey sey ye hadees Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursal tareeqe sey bhi aai hai. 3- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : Raavi Jarrah bin Maleeh Sadooq hain aur Jarrah bin Zuhaak maqarib al hadees hain."
1810,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam (hijrat key baad) unkey ghar thehrey, un logon ney aap key liye takkaluf se bhara khana tayyar kiya jis mein kuchh in sabziyon (gandanaa waghera) mein sey thi, chunanche aap ney isey khana napasand kiya aur Sahaba sey farmaya : ''tum log isey khaao, isliye ke main tumhari tarah nahin hun, main darta hun ke main apney rafeeq (Jibreel) ko takleef pahuchaun.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- Umme Ayub abu-Ayyub Ansari ki biwi hain."
1811,"lahsun halal rizq hai. Abu Khalda ka naam Khalid bin Dinar hai, wo muhaddeseen key nazdik bharosemand hain, unhoney Anas bin Malik sey mulaqat ki hai aur un sey hadees suni hai, Abul Aaliya ka naam Rafeea' hai aur ye Rafeea' Riyaahi hain, Abdur-Rehman bin Mehdi kehtey hain : Abu Khalda eik nek musalman they."
1812,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''(sotey waqt) darwaza band kar lo, mishkeeze ka munh baandh do , bartanon ko ondha kar do ya unhen dhanp do aur chiragh bujha do , isliye ke shetan kisi band darwazey ko nahin kholta hai aur na kisi bandhan aur bartan ko kholta hai, (aur chiragh isliye bujha do ke) choohaa logon ka ghar jala deta hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Jabir sey dusri sanadon sey bhi aai hai. 3- is bab mein ibne-Umar , Abu-Hurera aur ibne-Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1813,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''sotey waqt apney gharon mein) jalti hui) aag na chhodo.''Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1814,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney do khajoor eik sath khaney sey mana farmaya yahan tak ke apney sath khaney waley ki ijazat hasil kar ley. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Saad Mola abu-Bakar sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1815,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jis ghar mein khajoor nahin us ghar key log bhookey hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey Hisham bin Urwa ki riwayat sey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- mainey Imam Bukhari sey is hadees key barey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : Yahya bin Hassan key ilawa main nahin janta hun kisi ney isey riwayat kiya hai. 3- is bab mein abu-Raafey ki biwi Sulami Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1816,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''beshak Allah Taala us bandey sey razi hota hai jo eik luqma khata hai ya eik ghoont peeta hai, to is par Allah ki tareef karta hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- Zakariya bin abi zyada sey isey kaee logon ney isi tarah riwayat kiya hai, hum isey sirf Zakariya bin Abi zyada ki riwayat sey jantey hain. 3- is bab mein Aqba bin Aamir , abu-Saeed , Aaisha , abu-Ayyub aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1817,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik kodhi ka haath pakda aur usey apney sath piyaley mein dakhil kya, phir farmaya : ''Allah ka naam ley kar is par bharosa rakhtey huye aur tawakkul kartey huye khaao.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf Yunus bin Muhammad ki riwayat sey jantey hain, jisey wo Mufazzal bin Fazala key wastey sey riwayat kartey hain. 2- ye Mufazzal bin Fazala eik Basraa Shaikh hain, Mufazzal bin Fazala eik doosrey Shaikh Basraa hain wo in sey ziyada bharosemand aur shohrat key Malik Raavi hain. 3- Shoba ney is hadees ko ba-tareeq : (حبيب بن الشهيد an ابن بريدة أن ابن عمر) riwayat kiya hai ke unhon (ibne-Umar) ney eik kodhi ka haath pakda, merey nazdik Shoba ki hadees ziyada sahih aur sabit hai."
1818,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''kafir saat aant mein khata hai aur momin eik aant mein khata hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , abu-Saeed , abu Basra Ghifaari, abu-Musa , jah'jaah Ghifaari, Memuna aur Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1819,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas eik kafir mehman aaya , aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney uskey liye bakri ka doodh dohney ka hukm diya, bakri dohi gaee , wo doodh pi gaya, phir dusri dohi gaee , us ko bhi pi gaya, is tarah wo saat bakriyon ka doodh pi gaya, phir kal subah ho kar wo Islam ley aaya , Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney uskey liye eik bakri (dohney ka ( hukm diya, wo dohi gaee, wo uska doodh pi gaya, phir aap ney dusri ka hukm diya to wo uska pura doodh na pi saka, (is par) Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''momin eik aant mein peeta hai aur kafir saat aanton mein peeta hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Suhel ki riwayat sey Hasan sahih gharib hai."
1820,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''do aadmiyon ka khana teen aadmiyon key liye aur teen aadmiyon ka khana chaar aadmiyon key liye kafi hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Jabir aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''eik aadmi ka khana do aadmiyon ko kifaayat kar jaeyga, do aadmi ka khana chaar aadmiyon ko kifaayat kar jaeyga aur chaar aadmi ka khana aath aadmiyon ko kifaayat kar jaeyga.''  3- is bab mein Jabir aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1821,"un sey tiddi key barey mein puchha gaya, to unhoney kaha : mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath chhe ghazwey kiye aur tiddi khatey rahey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ko Sufiyan bin Uena ney Abu Yaafur sey isi tarah riwayat kiya hai aur kaha hai : ''chhe ghazwey kiye.''  2- aur Sufiyan Sory aur kaee logon ney Abu Yaafur sey ye hadees riwayat ki hai aur kaha hai : ''saat ghazwey kiye.''"
1822,"hamney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath saat ghazawaat kiye aur tiddi khatey rahey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Shoba ney bhi isey Abu Yaafur key wastey sey ibne-Abi Aufi sey riwayat kiya hai, unhoney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath kaee ghazawaat kiye aur tiddi khatey rahey."
1823,"jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam tiddiyon par bad dua kartey to kehtey :« اللهم أهلك الجراد اقتل كباره وأهلك صغاره وأفسد بيضه واقطع دابره وخذ بأفواههم an معاشنا وأرزاقنا إنك سميع الدعاء » ''Allah ! tiddiyon ko halak kar dey , badon ko maar dey , chhoton ko tabah kar dey , in key andon ko kharab kar dey, inka jad sey khatima kar dey, aur hamarey muaash aur rizq tabah karney sey inkey munh rok ley, beshak to dua ko sun-ney wala hai.''  eik aadmi ney puchha : Allah key Rasool ! Allah key lashkaron mein sey eik lashkar ko jad sey khatam karney ki bad dua kaisey kar rahey hain? Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''wo samandar mein machli ki chheenk hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 2- Musa bin Muhammad bin Ibrahim Taimi key barey mein muhaddeseen ney kalam kiya hai, in sey gharib aur munkir riwaayatein kasrat sey hain, in key baap Muhammad bin Ibrahim  bharosemand hain aur Madina key rehney waley hain."
1824,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam gandagi khaney waley janwer key gosht khaney aur unka doodh peeney sey mana farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- Sory ney isey (an ibne-Abi Najeeh an Mujahid an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam) ki sanad sey mursal tareeqe sey riwayat ki hai. 3- is bab mein Abdullah bin Abbas sey bhi hadees marvi (riwayat hui) hai.
1825,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney « مجثمة » aur gandagi khaney waley janwer key doodh aur mashk key munh sey pani peeney sey mana farmaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Muhammad bin Bashaar kehtey hain : hum sey ibn Adi ney (an Saeed bin abi Aruba an Qatada an Akrama an ibne-Abbas an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) ki sanad sey isi jaisi hadees bayan ki hai. 3- is bab mein Abdullah bin Amr sey bhi hadees marvi (riwayat hui) hai.
1826,"main abu-Musa key paas gaya, wo murghi kha rahey they, kaha : qarib ho jaao aur khaao isliye ke mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko isey khatey dekha hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai, Zahdam sey ye hadees dusri sanadon sey bhi aai hai, hum isey sirf Zahdam hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
1827,Mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko murgh ka gosht khatey dekha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is hadees mein kuch aur baaten bhi hain. 3- Ayub Sakhtiyaan ney bhi is hadees ko : (عن القاسم التميمي an أبي قلابة an زهدم) ki sanad sey riwayat ki hai.
1828,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath hubaari (surkhaab) ka gosht khaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain. 3- Ibrahim bin umr bin Safina sey ibne-Abi Fidya ney bhi riwayat ki hai, inhen Bareed bin umr bin Safina bhi kaha gaya hai."
1829,"unhoney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki khidmat mein bhuni dast pesh ki, aap ney is mein sey khaya , phir namaz key liye khadey huye aur wuzu nahin kya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Haris , Mughira aur abu-Raafey (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1830,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main tek laga kar nahin khata.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- hum isey sirf Ali bin Aqmar ki riwayat sey jantey hain, Ali bin Aqmar sey is hadees ko Zakariya bin abi zyada , Sufiyan bin Saeed Sory aur kaee logon ney riwayat kiya hai, Shoba ney ye hadees Sufiyan Sory sey Ali bin Aqmar key wastey sey riwayat ki hai. 3- is bab mein Ali , Abdullah bin Amr aur Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1831,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam meethi chiz aur shehad ko pasand kartey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- isey Ali bin Mus'hir ney bhi Hisham bin Urwa key wastey sey riwayat ki hai. 3- hadees mein is sey ziyada baaten hain.
1832,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab tum mein sey koi gosht khareedey to is mein (pakaatey waqt) shorbaa (salan) ziyada kar ley, isliye ke agar wo gosht na paa sakey to usey shorbaa mil jaey, wo bhi do gosht mein sey eik gosht hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein Abu-Zar sey bhi riwayat hai, 2- hum isey sirf isi sanad sey Muhammad bin Fazaa ki riwayat sey jantey hain, Muhammad bin Fazaa Muabbir (yani khuwab ki tabeer bayan karney waley) hain, in key barey mein Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Harab ney kalam kiya hai. 3- ye hadees gharib hai."
1833,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' tum logon mein sey koi shakhs kisi bhi nek kaam ko haqeer na samjhey , agar koi nek kaam na mil sakey to apney bhai sey muskura kar miley padhi. , aur agar tum gosht kharido ya haandi pakaao to shorbaa ( salan ( badha lo aur is mein sey thoda sa apney padosi ko dey do.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Shoba ney bhi isey abu-Imraan Jawni key wastey sey riwayat kiya hai."
1834,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' mardon mein sey bahut sarey mard darja kamaal ko pahunchey padhi. aur aurton mein sey sirf Maryam binte Imran aur Firon ki biwi Aasiya darja kamaal ko pahunchin aur tamam aurton par Aaisha ko isi tarah fazilat hasil hai jis tarah tamam khaanon par sareed ko.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Aaisha aur Anas sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1835,"merey baap ney meri shaadi ki aur logon ko bulaaya, un mein Safwan bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they, unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''gosht ko daant sey noch kar khaao isliye ke wo ziyada jald hazam hota hai, aur lazeez hota hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ko hum sirf Abdul-Karim ki riwayat sey jantey hain aur Abdul-Karim Al Muallim key hafizey key barey mein ehle-ilm ney kalam kiya hai, kalam karney walon mein Ayub Sakhtiyaan bhi hain. 2- is bab mein Aaisha aur Abu-Hurera Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1836,"Unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko dekha ke aap ney bakri ki dast ka gosht chhuri sey kaataa , aur is mein sey khaya , phir namaz key liye tashrif ley gaey aur wuzu nahin kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Mughira bin Shoba sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1837,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki khidmat mein gosht laya gaya aur aap ko dast pesh ki gaee , aap ko dast bahut pasand thi, chunanche aap ney isey daant sey noch kar khaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Masood , Aaisha , Abdullah bin Jaafar aur abu-Ubaida (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain. 3- abu-Hayyaan ka naam Yahya bin Saeed bin Hayyan hai aur abu-Zara'a bin Amr bin Jareer ka naam Harm hai."
1838,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko dast ka gosht ziyada pasand nahin tha, lekin aap ko ye kabhi kabhi milta tha, isliye aap usey khaney mein jaldi kartey they kyonkey wo doosrey gosht key muqabley mein jaldi galta hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees gharib hai hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
1839,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' sirka kya hi behtareen salan hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein Aaisha aur Umme-Haani sey bhi ahadees aai hain.
1840,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' sirka kya hi behtareen salan hai ''.
1841,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam merey ghar tashrif laye aur farmaya : '' kya tumharey paas ( khaney key liye ( kuch hai? ''main ney arz kya : nahin, sirf roti key chand khushk tukdey aur sirka hai, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' usey laao , wo ghar salan ka mohtaj nahin hai jis mein sirka ho ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan gharib hai, hum isey is sanad sey sirf Umme-Haani ki riwayat sey jantey hain, 2- Umme-Haani ki wafat Ali bin abi Talib key kuch dino baad hui, 3- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey is hadees key barey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : Shaaby ka samaa, Umme-Haani sey mein nahin janta hun, 4- mainey phir puchha : aap ki nazar mein abu-Hamza Sabit bin abi Safiya kaisey hain? unhoney kaha : Ahmed bin Hanbal ka unkey barey mein kalam hai aur merey nazdik wo maqaribul-hadees hain."
1842,Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''sirka kya hi behtareen salan hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadeese-Mubarak bin Saeed ki hadees sey ziyada sahih hai.
1843,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam taza khajoor key sath tarbuz khatey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, 2- baaz logon ney isey « an Hisham bin Urwa an Abeeh an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » ki sanad sey mursal tariqa sey riwayat ki hai, is mein Aaisha key wasta ka zikr nahin kya hai, Yazeed bin Ruman ney is hadees ko Urwa key wastey sey Aaisha sey riwayat ki hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Anas sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1844,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam taza khajoor key sath kakdi khatey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih gharib hai, 2- hum isey sirf Ibrahim bin Saad ki riwayat sey jantey hain."
1845,"qabila uraina key kuch log Madina aaye, unhen Madina ki aab o huwa raas nahin aai, isliye Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney unhen sadqey key oonton mein bheja aur farmaya : ''oonton ka peshab aur doodh piyo''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai, 2- ye hadees dusri sanadon sey bhi Anas sey aai hai, abu-Qulaba ney isey Anas sey riwayat ki hai aur Saeed bin abi Aruba ney bhi usey Qatada key wastey sey Anas sey riwayat ki hai."
1846,"mainey Torat mein padha hai ke '' khaney ki barkat khaney key baad wuzu karney mein hai'', mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey usey bayan kya aur jo kuch Torat mein padha tha usey bataya to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' khaney ki barkat khaney sey pehley aur uskey baad wuzu karney mein hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ko hum sirf Qais bin Rabee ki riwayat sey jantey hain, 2- aur Qais bin Rabee hadees bayan karney mein zaeef hain, padhi. 3- is bab mein Anas aur Abu-Hurera Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1847,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam pakhana sey tashrif laye, to aap ki khidmat mein khana pesh kya gaya, Sahaba ney arz kya : kya aap key liye wuzu ka pani laeyn ? aap ney farmaya : '' mujhey namaz key liye jatey waqt wuzu ka hukm diya gaya hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- usey Amr bin Dinar ney Saeed bin Huweris key wastey sey ibne-Abbas sey riwayat ki hai, 3- Ali bin Madini kehtey hain : Yahya bin Saeed ney kaha : Sufiyan Sory khaney sey pehley haath dhona makrooh samajhtey they, wo piyala key nichey chapati rakhna bhi makrooh samajhtey they."
1848,"Banu Murra bin Ubaid ney apni zakat ka maal dey kar mujhey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki khidmat mein bheja , main aap key paas Madina aaya to aap ko muhajrin aur ansaar key bech betha paya, phir aap ney mera haath pakda aur mujhey Umme-Salma (Raziallahu Anha) key ghar ley gaey aur puchha : '' khaney key liye kuch hai? '' chunanche eik piyala laya gaya jis mein ziyada sareed ( shorbey mein tar ki hui roti) aur botiyaan thin, hum usey khaney key liye mutawajjeh huye, main piyaley key kinaron par apna haath maarney laga aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam apney samney sey khaney lagey, phir aap ney apney baaein hath sey mera daayan haath pakad kar farmaya : ''Ikrash ! eik jagah sey khaao isliye ke ye eik hi qism ka khana hai'' , phir hamarey paas eik tabaq laya gaya jis mein mukhtalif qism ki khajuren thin, main apney samney sey khaney laga, aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka haath tabaq mein ghoomney laga, aap ney farmaya : ''Ikrash! jahan sey chaho khaao, isliye ke ye eik qism ka nahin hai'' , phir hamarey paas pani laya gaya, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney apney dono haath dhoey aur hatheliyon ki tari sey chehrey, bazu aur sar par masah kya aur farmaya : '' Ikrash ! ye aag par paki hui chiz khaney key baad ka wuzu hai ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- hum isey sirf Alaa bin Fazal ki riwayat sey jantey hain, Alaa is hadees ki riwayat karney mein munfarid hain, 2- hum Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey Ikrash ki sirf isi hadees ko jantey hain."
1849,"main Anas bin Malik key paas gaya, wo kadu kha rahey they, aur keh rahey they : aey bail! kis qadr to mujhey pasand hai ! kyonkey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam tujhey pasand kartey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Hakim bin Jabir sey bhi riwayat hai jisey Hakim apney walid sey riwayat kartey hain."
1850,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko dekha ke aap Rakabi mein dhoond rahey they yani kadu, us waqt sey mein usey hamesha pasand karta hun. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ye hadees Anas sey dusri sanadon sey bhi aai hai, 3- riwayat ki gaee hai ke Anas ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key samney kadu dekha to aap sey puchha : ye kya hai? aap ney farmaya : '' ye kadu hai hum us sey apney khaney ki miqdaar badhaatey hain''."
1851,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''zaitun ka tel khaao aur isey (jism par) lagaao , isliye ke wo Mubarak darkht hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees ko hum sirf abdur-Razzaaq ki riwayat sey jantey hain jisey wo Maamar sey riwayat kartey hain. 2- Abdur-Razzaaq is hadees ki riwayat karney mein muztarib (pareshan) hain, kabhi wo isey marfoo riwayat kartey hain aur kabhi shak key sath riwayat kartey huye kehtey hain ke main samajhta hun isey umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat kiya hai, aur kabhi kehtey hain : Zaid bin Aslam sey riwayat hai, wo apney baap sey aur wo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursal tareeqe sey riwayat kartey hain."
1852,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''zaitun ka tel khaao aur isey (jism par) lagaao isliye ke wo Mubarak darkht hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai, hum isey sirf Sufiyan Sory ki riwayat sey Abdullah bin Esa key wastey sey jantey hain."
1853,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab tum mein sey kisi ka khaadim tumharey khaney ki garmi aur dhuwan bardasht karey , to ( Malik ko chahiye ke khatey waqt ( uska haath pakad kar apney sath bitha ley, agar wo inkar karey to eik luqma ley kar hi usey khila dey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1854,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''salam ko aam karo aur isey phailao , khana khaao aur kafiron ka sar maaro (yani un sey jihad karo) jannat key waris bin jaaogey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Abu-Hurera key wastey sey ibne Ziyad ki riwayat sey Hasan sahih gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Abdullah bin Amr , ibne-Umar , Anas , Abdullah bin Salam , Abdur-Rehman bin Aaesh aur Shureh bin Haani (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, Shureh bin Haani ney apney walid sey riwayat ki hai."
1855,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Rehman ki ibadat karo, khana khaoo aur salam ko aam karo aur isey phailao , jannat mein salamti key sath dakhil ho'o gey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1856,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''raat ka khana khaao chaahe eik mutthi raddi khajoor hi kyon na ho, isliye ke raat ka khana chhodna budhapey ka sabab hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees munkir hai. 2- hum isey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain, Anbasaa hadees bayan karney mein zaeef hain aur abdul-Malik bin Alaq majhool hain."
1857,"wo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas gaey, aap key paas khana rakha tha, aap ney farmaya : '' betey ! qarib ho jaao ,Bismillah padho aur apney dahiney haath sey jo tumharey qarib hai usey khaao.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hisham bin Urwa sey :(عن أبي وجزة السعدي an رجل من مزينة an عمر ابن أبي سلمة) ki sanad sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai, is hadees ki riwayat karney mein Hisham bin Urwa key shagirdon ka ikhtilaf hai."
1858,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab tum logon mein sey koi khana khaye to (Bismillah) padh ley , agar shuru mein bhool jaey to ye kahey (بسم الله في أوله وآخره)."
1859,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''shetan bahut taadne aur chaatney wala hai, us sey khud ko bachaao, jo shakhs raat guzaarey aur uskey haath mein chiknai ki boo ho, phir usey koi bula pahunchey to wo sirf apney aap ko bura bhala kahey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai. 2- ye hadees (Suhail ibne-Abi Saleh an Abeeh an abi Huraira an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam) ki sanad sey bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai."
1860,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo shakhs raat guzaarey aur uskey haath mein chiknai ki boo ho phir usey koi bula pahunchey to wo sirf apney aap ko bura bhala kahey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai, hum isey Aamash ki riwayat sey sirf isi sanad sey jantey hain."
